<div style="font-family: Georgia, serif; max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; color: #1c2015; line-height: 1.6;">
  <h1 style="font-size: 28px; color: #3a4a1e; margin: 0 0 16px;">
    Hi <%= @request.first_name %>,
  </h1>

  <p>Your free copy request just landed in our queue. Thank you for asking — the books are yours.</p>

  <p style="background: #f5f0dc; border-left: 3px solid #a3bf64; padding: 16px 20px; margin: 24px 0; font-style: italic;">
    <strong style="display: block; margin-bottom: 8px;">What you asked for:</strong>
    <%= @request.book_summary %>
  </p>

  <p><strong>Shipping to:</strong><br>
    <%= @request.full_name %><br>
    <%= @request.address_line_1 %><br>
    <% if @request.address_line_2.present? %><%= @request.address_line_2 %><br><% end %>
    <%= @request.city %>, <%= @request.state_province %> <%= @request.postal_code %><br>
    <%= @request.country %>
  </p>

  <p>We'll be in touch when the books are on the way.</p>

  <p style="margin-top: 32px; font-style: italic; color: #a3bf64;">
    — <%= ENV.fetch('SITE_NAME', 'SystemOrEcosystem') %>
  </p>
</div>
